Hardware-safety note
--------------------
symaira-tune can read and (in future versions / the Pro tier) adjust low-level
Mac hardware state such as display brightness, fan speed, and battery charging.
All write paths are clamped to safe ranges and never disable the firmware's
thermal protection. Use at your own risk; see the warranty disclaimer in LICENSE.

